104
00:06:12,655 --> 00:06:14,987
- Okay, we'll have lunch.
- It's not lunchtime.

105
00:06:18,361 --> 00:06:19,919
That's his head exploding.

106
00:06:22,498 --> 00:06:24,261
Judith, I can change.

107
