You know who wrote that song?

145
00:09:08,264 --> 00:09:10,095
- Your uncle Charlie wrote that.
- No lie?

146
00:09:10,166 --> 00:09:12,566
<i>If I was to lie, I'd say I wrote
Stairway to Heaven,</i>

147
00:09:12,635 --> 00:09:14,102
not the Maple Loops song.

148
00:09:16,305 --> 00:09:18,671
- You two are really good together.
- Thank you.

149
00:09:19,442 --> 00:09:21,000
