150
00:09:22,011 --> 00:09:24,741
- No, I'm not married.
- What a shame.

151
00:09:29,151 --> 00:09:32,518
Wow. You're even better than a dog.

152
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:40,356
Dr. Bloom? Yes, this is Alan Harper.

153
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:44,794
My wife and I need to cancel our marriage
counseling appointment for this afternoon.

154
00:09:46,369 --> 00:09:48,166
Yes, well, something came up.

155
00:09:49,472 --> 00:09:52,305
Well, it's kind of personal. I mean...

156
00:09:53,042 --> 00:09:55,602
Well, yeah,
I know the point of these things is...

157
00:09:57,980 --> 00:09:59,277
I've got to go.

158
00:10:00,650 --> 00:10:02,709
- Hello?
- Is Charlie home?

159
00:10:02,985 --> 00:10:05,715
No. I'm Charlie's brother. Can I help you?

160
00:10:07,223 --> 00:10:10,556
Hi, Charlie's brother. I'm Rose.

161
00:10:10,826 --> 00:10:12,657
