from the door.

165
00:10:24,740 --> 00:10:26,071
You know what I mean?

166
00:10:26,676 --> 00:10:28,337
Sure. Come on in.

167
00:10:33,749 --> 00:10:35,307
Yeah, I can smell him.

168
00:10:37,553 --> 00:10:38,918
