you threw out of the house

234
00:14:23,445 --> 00:14:25,413
four and a half days ago,
let me tell you that.

235
00:14:25,481 --> 00:14:26,675
Jake's doing fine.

236
00:14:26,749 --> 00:14:29,081
You were concerned about him
being around my brother,

237
00:14:29,151 --> 00:14:30,812
but Charlie's great with kids.

238
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,953
All right, last card, down and dirty.

239
00:14:35,758 --> 00:14:36,918
King's bet.

240
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,125
- $1.
- I'm in.

241
00:14:39,228 --> 00:14:40,422
In.

